to relate with Paul's words

00:03:41.180 --> 00:03:45.340
or what you said, this
deepened a relationship of mine

00:03:45.340 --> 00:03:48.390
in some way, or this made
me less afraid to die,

00:03:48.390 --> 00:03:50.810
which is quite a
profound thing to say.

00:03:50.810 --> 00:03:55.880
And I think that would have
meant a lot to Paul as well.

00:03:55.880 --> 00:03:57.720
So that's been really exciting.

00:03:57.720 --> 00:04:00.610
