00:04:14.960 --> 00:04:16.899
So I think just the
feeling of connecting

00:04:16.899 --> 00:04:18.410
with people over suffering.

00:04:18.410 --> 00:04:19.980
It's not something
any of us wants,

00:04:19.980 --> 00:04:24.910
