multiple organ systems,

00:12:01.400 --> 00:12:02.990
the diagnosis was clear.

00:12:02.990 --> 00:12:04.210
The room was quiet.

00:12:04.210 --> 00:12:07.450
Lucy told me she loved me. 'I
don't want to die,' I said.

00:12:07.450 --> 00:12:09.520
I told her to remarry,
that I couldn't bear

00:12:09.520 --> 00:12:11.080
the thought of her being alone.

00:12:11.080 --> 00:12:15.430
I told her we should refinance
the mortgage immediately."

