00:12:29.210 --> 00:12:31.580
And this is a recurring
theme of striving

00:12:31.580 --> 00:12:33.566
that comes across so
many times in the book.

00:12:33.566 --> 00:12:35.440
I wonder if you could
elaborate on that.

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:36.315
LUCY KALANITHI: Sure.

00:12:36.315 --> 00:12:37.162
Yeah.

00:12:37.162 --> 00:12:38.370
And it's kind of interesting.

00:12:38.370 --> 00:12:40.750
So literally, one of
the first things he said

00:12:40.750 --> 00:12:43.200
